data.description: Cape Cod Style home in the heart of Danville! This home offers 4 bedrooms with 2 being on the main level & 2 upper. Main floor laundry, Updated Kitchen and 2 living areas with flex space for dining. Great Room is large in size and includes a wood burning fireplace and leads to the attached 2 car garage. Upper 3rd & 4th bedrooms offer plenty of room to spread out. So many options with this homes layout! No HOA and walking distance to parks, farmers market, theatre and all Danville has to offer. Home sits on a corner lot with small backyard which would make a Great Bistro styled area! Home includes an oversized 2 car attached garage.
